GYROMEZES FINAL WEBSITE

This folder contains the final static website files.

For GitHub Pages:
1. Open this folder.
2. Upload the CONTENTS of this folder to GitHub:
   - index.html
   - assets folder
   - README_UPLOAD.txt
3. Do not upload the ZIP file itself.
4. Do not upload the parent folder as a folder inside GitHub.
5. The index.html file must be at the root of the repository.

The site is static HTML/CSS/JS. No build command is needed.
